					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8517077#post-4070745</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8517077/scp-4248#post-4070745</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 29 Nov 2018 02:42:04 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>not_a_seagull</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3009022</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well, they decided to change it from 5 because 5 is associated with Fifthism and all that nasty stuff. So they changed it, just to flex on all of those Fifthists.</p> <p>But why did they decide to change it to a 7, instead of a less superstitious number, and why was it on the same line as Nu-7, another MTF? You see, it’s a parallel universe, and— you know what, I’ve already written myself into a corner here, and I’ll just fix the typo.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
