						 <p>Alright, this is a pretty big departure in style for me. My usual go-to is medium-length with an interview log, and this is really the first time I've executed an exploration log in a mainlist skip.</p> <p>Anyways, this was written for <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541808801" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" >Rimple</a></span>'s <a href="http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/collab:draft-swap-2">Draft Swap</a>, and I got <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3213383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541808801" alt="OthellotheCat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3213383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" >OthellotheCat</a></span>'s draft, which was an alphabet book.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meserach" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1507289&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541808801" alt="Meserach" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1507289)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meserach" >Meserach</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541808801" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" >DrChandra</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541808801" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" >Rounderhouse</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541808801" alt="FloppyPhoenix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" >FloppyPhoenix</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3213383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541808801" alt="OthellotheCat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3213383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" >OthellotheCat</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bolterpyre" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4062444&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541808801" alt="Bolterpyre" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4062444)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bolterpyre" >Bolterpyre</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kakroom" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2198340&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541808801" alt="Kakroom" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2198340)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kakroom" >Kakroom</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><im